==English==

===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|h₂eHs}}
From {{der|en|fr|aride}} or directly from {{der|en|la|āridus||dry, arid, parched}},<ref>{{R:Lexico}}</ref> confer its synonymous contracted form {{m|la|ardus}}. Originally from the verb {{m|la|āreo||I am dry, I am parched}}, akin to {{m|la|ārdeō||I am on fire, I burn}}.

